<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id7a12099d-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id7a12099e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2018—Subsec. (a)(3), (4). <ref href="/us/pl/115/334">Pub. L. 115–334</ref> added par. (3) and redesignated former par. (3) as (4).</p>
</note>
</notes>
